{"tid":129984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來曾蔭權四兄妹咁猛料","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T18:09:30.000Z","uid":51615,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56498a0ed28b5eef6af86e6505ec1cf806d76684","tid":129984,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"大哥曾蔭權。。香港特首<br />\n二佬曾蔭培。。警務署長<br />\n細佬曾蔭瑄。。生意佬<br />\n細妹曾璟璇。。渣打揸fit人<br />\n<br />\n好癲，點解幾兄弟妹都咁勁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a945e8c45e0246401a1b6c5192e8d4701876f9","tid":129984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬曾蔭瑄。。生意佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未聽過<br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b28a7fb6dee0eba6246b819757ebb0eeced972","tid":129984,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"有幾勁？靠關係，一個帶一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a428221a3193c99ea47eb1130db6431585db3cb0","tid":129984,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細佬曾蔭瑄。。生意佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未聽過<br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三弟曾蔭煊及五弟曾蔭荃，在1989年共同創辦Phase Technology高科技公司，主要是設計、製造與生產測試石油質量的儀器。曾蔭荃說，公司創立時，他負責化學工程部分，哥哥負責市場經營，兩人分工合作。目前全世界80%的煉油廠，都是使用該公司的產品。<br />\n曾蔭煊和曾蔭荃榮膺2007年度卑詩省新加拿大企業家大獎（BC New-Canadian Entrepreneur Awards）。曾蔭荃領獎時勉勵有創業理想的新移民，要有毅力和信心，遇困難不退縮的精神。<br />\n曾蔭荃曾在亞省大學修讀化學工程學位，後赴美國康奈爾大學（Cornell University）攻讀，獲化學工程碩士學位。<br />\n雷曼兄弟（Lehman Brothers）迷債事件中，曾蔭煊的妻子是苦主，有報道指弟婦提早獲得賠償，曾蔭煊特別發聲明指與兄長曾蔭權無關。<br />\n曾蔭權一門多傑，除了開科技公司兩兄弟外，二弟曾蔭培是前香港警隊「一哥」；四弟曾蔭藩在加拿大麥吉爾大學（McGill University）任大學教授，研究人類細胞染色體；細妹曾璟璇任職香港渣打銀行，曾先後擔任中國區總裁及大中華區主席"},{"pid":"a86fb8c7c95e13fac0c7b61e75086280736ea856","tid":129984,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"強如蔭權<br />\n仍然克制唔到<br />\n華人貪婪基因"},{"pid":"937eadc28c5ddb0d73e30f8846ba264898ee588c","tid":129984,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"925c3613514369e0d78b05f69d2c0adcfe9ee3aa","tid":129984,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"好撚屈機<br />\n<br />\n我發覺上流社會其實大部分人都係有親戚關係<br />\n<br />\n係wiki到睇睇下就知"},{"pid":"88a47f083c3abd344d6424d09ad4ff96f645f0c1","tid":129984,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"曾家都幾威<br />\n<br />\n修身齊家治國都做齊"},{"pid":"6c3efa212965b9194c4fa69f22c9b55a95d58be1","tid":129984,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"佢個仔都做到醫生，證明基因「係精神嘅」"},{"pid":"df226dc1af6c504ae46ce278c98d3f04ce56ec0f","tid":129984,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"仲要全家係公屋大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f70461d731b3e7485f993e4859da53d1934b7d","tid":129984,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要全家係公屋大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以養成曾特少少都貪 好聽就慳家 唔好聽就貪心"},{"pid":"1c0b7b65d0f214bd9ea5b6101a7e5d789a29f749","tid":129984,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要全家係公屋大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955218d31d94b9fc1810bf2bef4bfdf9d24e6c53","tid":129984,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:19:47.000Z","msg